I brought this movie for my daughter and she loves it. She is a bratz doll fan. She watched this movie over and over and over again. I may need to order another one in case she wears this one out.
THIS WAS A GREAT MOVIE I JUST WISHED IT WAS LONGER, I AM PLEASED WITH THE SERVICE AND PRODUCT. THANKS

I bought this dvd for my 6 year old daughter, she just love,love the bratzs. She has watch this movie over 20 times, I have to say give it a rest. The movie is about Cloe, Jade, Sasha and Yasmin, getting ready to go on a reality show hosted by their friend Byron. The reality show is about young girls fashion designers modeling in a glitzy New York fashion show. The prize for the winner is diamond studded Go-Go boots. On the way to the reality show the bratz encounter a hunted town, mysterious traveler, a fashion designer wannabe, so they have to over come all these things so they don't miss the competition. SO you have to buy the dvd to find out what happended at the end. I recommend this dvd for all the kids who love the bratz, trust me this movie don't disappoint.
My kids like these dolls and the movies. This is a fun movie. We had a sleepover and all the kids watched over and over.

My six year old granddaughter is a Big Bratz fan, and this dvd fits perfectly in her collection. We watch it all the time along with her other favorites. It's a good movie and is enjoyable for all ages.
Awesome I can't believe this came out in 2006 but it's still awesome!! Fun movie and it's so stylin!!! Bratz rock!
